  "id" : "api/common/CurrencyPipe",
  "title" : "CurrencyPipe",
  "contents" : "<article>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 class=\"no-toc\" id=\"currencypipe\">CurrencyPipe</h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label pipe\">pipe</label>\n    \n    \n    \n    <span class=\"version\"></span>\n  </header>\n\n  \n  <!-- INFO BAR -->\n<section class=\"info-bar\">\n\n<table class=\"is-full-width\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4wfc14obst93bim1zva6hqjl0\">npm 包</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/common\">@angular/common</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dkuxw56x8curh875ge5tvqede\">模块</th>\n  <td><code>import { <a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">CurrencyPipe</a> } from <a href=\"api/common\">'@angular/common'</a>;</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n  <th data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ee4tba1a8v4m1low7rnv25o9l\">源码</th>\n  <td><a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/common/src/pipes/number_pipe.ts#L96-L157\">common/src/pipes/number_pipe.ts</a></td>\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n  <th>NgModule</th>\n  <td><a href=\"api/common/CommonModule\"><code>CommonModule</code></a></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n<div class=\"what-it-does info-banner\">\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dw2jjfcefffe5w6rkk6vtnrma\">使用区域设置规则将数字格式化为货币。</p>\n\n</div>\n\n  \n  \n  \n  \n<section class=\"how-to-use\">\n  <h2 id=\"how-to-use\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cflu95twzi71qd095ghj9h0y7\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>使用方法</h2>\n  <p><code>number_expression | currency[:currencyCode[:display[:digitInfo[:locale]]]]</code></p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ar5q09mdsagdppsbze96eagxl\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>说明</h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e68t0z81gvbv50yfo74u7ln95\">使用 \n<code>currency</code> 将数字格式化为货币。</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"cy4mvqwd1ff6v6ddhgm8ydsd\"><code>currencyCode</code> 是 \n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_4217\">ISO 4217</a> 货币代码，例如 \n<code>USD</code> 代表美元，\n<code>EUR</code> 代表欧元。</li>\n<li>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"d8cp87x5jv7vjxijlwypjm6dp\"><code>display</code> 指示是否显示货币符号或代码。</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6jr2zobym3axwuuld0zgy3r6s\"><code>code</code>：使用代码（例如 \n<code>USD</code>）。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ezqqsx71rsszgyccv0xshjdon\"><code>symbol</code>（默认）：使用符号（例如 \n<code>$</code>）。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dfl03087npkyv9b1z3ujc96hv\"><code>symbol-narrow</code>：某些国家/地区为其货币使用两种符号，一种是常规符号，另一种是窄符号（例如，加拿大元 CAD 的符号是 \n<code>CA$</code>，窄符号是 \n<code>$</code>）。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"b40l73qkji1bt5zrei0tgimb0\">布尔值（从 v5 开始已弃用）：\n<code>true</code> 代表符号，\n<code>false</code> 代表 \n<code>code</code>。如果所选货币没有窄符号，则将使用常规符号。</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8x4i739jwk9e6fcb1xnyiz3tr\"><code>digitInfo</code> 详细说明请参见 \n<a href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe\"><code>DecimalPipe</code></a>。</li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1d3qlmx7iwf7mbo3kofbyut1m\"><code>locale</code> 是一个 \n<code>string</code>，定义要使用的语言环境（默认情况下使用当前的 \n<a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\"><code>LOCALE_ID</code></a>）</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"example\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_confirmed data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"lzz2v4ucg07faxnpe2bu1wa1\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i>范例</h3>\n<code-example>\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'currency-pipe',\n  template: `&lt;div&gt;\n    &lt;!--output '$0.259'--&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;A: {{<a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\" class=\"code-anchor\">a</a> | currency}}&lt;/p&gt;\n\n    &lt;!--output 'CA$0.26'--&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;A: {{<a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\" class=\"code-anchor\">a</a> | currency:'CAD'}}&lt;/p&gt;\n\n    &lt;!--output 'CAD0.26'--&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;A: {{<a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\" class=\"code-anchor\">a</a> | currency:'CAD':'code'}}&lt;/p&gt;\n\n    &lt;!--output 'CA$0,001.35'--&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;B: {{b | currency:'CAD':'symbol':'4.2-2'}}&lt;/p&gt;\n\n    &lt;!--output '$0,001.35'--&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;B: {{b | currency:'CAD':'symbol-narrow':'4.2-2'}}&lt;/p&gt;\n\n    &lt;!--output '0&nbsp;001,35&nbsp;CA$'--&gt;\n    &lt;p&gt;B: {{b | currency:'CAD':'symbol':'4.2-2':'fr'}}&lt;/p&gt;\n  &lt;/div&gt;`\n})\nexport class CurrencyPipeComponent {\n  <a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\" class=\"code-anchor\">a</a>: number = 0.259;\n  b: number = 1.3495;\n}\n\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n</section></article>\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - guide/i18n\n - guide/pipes\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/CommonModule\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe#currencypipe\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe#description\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe#example\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe#how-to-use\n - api/common/DecimalPipe\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/LOCALE_ID\n - api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\n - https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_4217\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/5.2.11/packages/common/src/pipes/number_pipe.ts#L96-L157\n - https://www.npmjs.com/package/@angular/common\n-->"
}